<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٢١٣-<span class="c5"> أَخْبَرَنِي حَرْبُ بْنُ إِسْمَاعِيلَ قَالَ:</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>سَأَلْتُ أَحْمَدَ عَنِ الْقَرَامِلِ؟<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">فَقَالَ:</span> تَشُدُّهُ الْمَرْأَةُ فِي أَطْرَافِ شَعْرِهَا وَلَا تَصِلُهُ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">قُلْتُ:</span> فَإِنْ كَانَ مِنْ صُوفٍ؟<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ:</span> وَإِنْ كَانَ مِنْ صَوفٍ فَإِنَّهَا لَا تَصِلُهُ بِشَعْرِهَا.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>